                            title.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Contact Data</strong>
                            includes billing address, email address and telephone numbers.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Financial Data</strong>
                            includes bank account and card payment details.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Transaction Data</strong>
                            includes details about payments to and from you and other details of
                            products and services you have purchased from us.
                        </li>
                        <li>
